OMG, what game are you playing? Warriors having better sustained DPS than wizards? Extra warriors being more welcome/valuable to a raid than wizards? Please tell me the majority of warriors here know this to be utterly false.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
You'd be surprised how often this inaccuracy is actually believed by both wizards and other classes. In the old days this was certainly true...doesn't come close any more since the balancing began.<br>
<br>
Back to the subject at hand...I really doubt that verant ever intended to have epics items so easily obtained by roving single or dual groups of any class, be they wizards or anyone else. I do think it's pretty mercenary to hold epic pieces ransom as it were by taking down mobs that have epic items on them.<br>
<br>
However, I think the warrior epic is so grossly underpowered considering the hassle to get it and other weapons in the game that I think that killing for a green scale is pretty worthless. As a class, warriors tend to be one of the more poor classes in my experience and the ones who look at the utility of the item are unlikely to pay large amounts for a scale even if they do have the cash.<br>
<br>
peace,<br>
Aielman KajiraLiege<br>
Birds of Prey, Prexus <p><center><img src="http://members.aol.com/azarielleeq/images/aieldon.jpg">
